Description: Manga-Downloader |Travis CI result|
        ===================================
        
        Universal assistant download manga.
        '''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
        
        Approximately 300 providers are available now.
        ''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
        
